# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DOCUMENTATION POLICY: Only commit key docs to GitHub
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ALLOWED in root:        README.md, CHANGELOG.md, CONTRIBUTING.md, SECURITY.md
# NOT allowed in root:    *.md (except above), *.docx, *.pdf, auto-generated docs
# docs/ folder is the official documentation library — all .md files tracked
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# All markdown files (except key documentation, whitelisted below)
*.md
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!SECURITY.md
!LICENSE
# docs/ folder is the official documentation library — all .md files tracked
!docs/*.md
!docs/**/*.md
# frontend/src/docs/ — in-app help content, must be committed
!frontend/src/docs/*.md
!frontend/src/docs/**/*.md

# All Microsoft Office documents and PDFs (local only)
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.pptx
*.pdf

# Auto-generated documentation (API docs, etc.)
docs/auto-generated/
generated/
_generated/

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
pip-wheel-metadata/
share/python-wheels/
